Upload: File A âœ“ (ID: 100), File B âœ— (Error)
Dropdown shows: File A, File B  âŒ (File B has no ID!)
```

**After:**
```
Upload: File A âœ“ (ID: 100), File B âœ— (Error)
Dropdown shows: File A only  âœ“ (File B filtered out!)
